================
 ``zope.intid``
================

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/zope.intid.svg
        :target: https://pypi.org/project/zope.intid/
        :alt: Latest release

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/pyversions/zope.intid.svg
